      About this item

      • Real-Time Energy Monitoring: Smart plugs track the real-time power, current, and voltage of your plug-in devices on Govee Home App. Supports reviewing data daily / weekly / monthly and up to 1 year to effectively save energy and reduce waste.
      • Stable WiFi & Bluetooth Connectivity: Connecting with Govee Home App via WiFi and Bluetooth to access the Smart Plug easily, even away, you can remotely control your home appliances and never come back to a dark home. Note: Do NOT support 5G Wi-Fi.
      • Convenient Voice Control: Free hands by using simple voice commands with Alexa and Google Assistant. Just once setting, you can enjoy coffee immediately after waking up and experience a leisurely morning. It's also a caring choice for the elderly.
      • Scheduling & Group Control: Smart plugs with timer help create detailed to the minute schedules power your appliances on/off automatically for helping save energy and money. And supports share on the Govee Home App to enjoy the smart life together.
      • Safe and Comfortable Smart Home: Govee plug not only fully FCC & ETL certified, but also made of fire-resistant materials. 15A 120V smart outlet is suitable for high-power appliances such as coffee maker, brings you a stable and safe life assistant.
      • This smart plug is ETL certified, ensuring it meets stringent safety standards for reliable and secure operation.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      5 out of 5 stars
      Absolutely Love These! Quirks Mentioned Below...
      4.75 out of 5.I am an avid Govee user. The app can be quirky, but if you have a DIY mindset at all, these quirks are easy to overcome. This switch is great: immediately connects, works over both wi-fi and bluetooth, and has timer functionality. The app is being constantly updated to fix bugs and improve automation.Some quirks to mention:(1) TIMERS always work; AUTOMATION requires wi-fi.A primary reason I purchased a few of these was to reboot my entire wi-fi network regularly at 5am, including mesh nodes, router, and some switches. The Govee app (as of version 6.5.02/866.0) has recently been encouraging me to move many of my scheduled lighting timers to the newer automation feature which (can be a little difficult to find: Shortcuts Panel >> Upper-right icon (looks like 3 squares and a circle) >> Auto-Run). For consistency, I decided to move my switches to this same system. I noticed, then, that the switches would never turn back on. After some troubleshooting, I discovered that using the timer feature (Home >> Tap the Device >> Timer) will work regardless of connection status, while the automation appears to require wi-fi. Not at all a dealbreaker for me, but I could see this causing frustrated returns for people wanting to reboot their network with this product. The lack of clarity here in when to use timers versus when to use automation, added to the lack of clarity of the location of the Automation section, is the reason for the 0.25 star reduction. I would consider this a perfect product, otherwise.(2) The size is indeed a little awkward... For power strips.Other reviews mention that the shape of these makes it difficult to not eat up two outlets on a power strip, however keep in mind that these are not really designed for that usage. They're designed for use in wall outlets, for which they are a perfect fit. That said, this is not at all a dealbreaker for me.
